### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Test Stats - Enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats/enrollment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Test Stats - Class Averages
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats/class-averages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Test Attendance - Today Rate
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/today-rate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Test Finance - Monthly Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/monthly-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Test Finance - Recovery Chart
GET {{baseUrl}}/finance/recovery-chart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Test Alerts - Open Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Test Calendar - Upcoming Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/calendar/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Test Health Check (no auth needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### 9. Login to get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "admin@school.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": false
}
